show.description:
A fiery chef and a smooth-talking restaurant manager find themselves in a battle of flavors and pride. But as the competition simmers, sparks of romance begin to blend with every recipe.
A heartwarming rom-com where food, secrets, and love make the perfect recipe for chaos and connection.
